description.en: The LSETH index token provides an equal-weighted basket of the leading liquid Ether staking rewards tokens. Benefits of LSETH’s index diversification include reduced volatility and risk, as well as automated token updates with no gas costs. The LSETH index composition will be updated and rebalanced automatically through decentralized, on-chain governance.
